definitions.definition: An old game in which a small piece of wood pointed at both ends is tipped , or struck with a stick or bat , to make it travel through the air as far as possible.
The wooden piece used in this game.

main_definition: ( uncountable ) An old game in which a small piece of wood pointed at both ends is tipped , or struck with a stick or bat , to make it travel through the air as far as possible.
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) The wooden piece used in this game.
